text: De Alleluia, and hwanan he come.
On hwilcere ðeode cwæð he hit?Responsio, On ebreisc.
Hwær cwæð he hine ærest? Betwux twam dunum, ða hattan Tabor and ermon.
Hwæt bið <hit> on ure leden?Alle, Saluum, lu, Me fac, la, Domine.
Hwæt bið hit on ure geðeode?Responsio, Hit bið, gehæle me, drihten.
And Hieronimus cwæð,Alle, Miserere, lu, Nobis, Ia, Domine.
Hwæt bið hit on ure leden?Responsio, Hit bið, miltsa us, Drihten.
Gregorius cwæð,Alle, pater, lu, Filius, Ia, Spiritus sanctus.
Hwæt bið on ure geðeode ðis? Hit bið,Alle, Fæder,lu, Sunu,Ia, Se halga gast.
